You are solely responsible for the information associated with Your Account and anything that happens related to Your Account.
You must maintain the security of your Account and promptly notify Codeaco support if you discover or suspect that someone has accessed your Account without your permission.
We recommend that you use a strong password that is used only with Codeaco.
title: You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account and for the activities on your account
